Generator Study
===============

Run on an FNAL GPVM inside the uboone container:

```
git clone https://github.com/njlane314/generators.git
cd generators
./.container.sh
```

Build the required stack:

```
./build_generators.sh
```

This builds GENIE 3.6.2, GiBUU 2025, NuWro, nusystematics, HepMC3, and
NUISANCE. Set up each new shell with:

```
source setup_generators.sh
```

The scoped analysis workflow is:

```
dry_run=1 analysis/bin/milestone_10k.sh
analysis/bin/milestone_10k.sh

dry_run=1 jobs_per_sample=10 events_per_job=200000 analysis/bin/submit_genie_grid_samples.sh
jobs_per_sample=10 events_per_job=200000 analysis/bin/submit_genie_grid_samples.sh

run_analysis=1 produce_samples=0 analysis/bin/pipeline.sh analysis/share/config/milestone_10k.env
```

GENIE grid outputs must be flattened into the manifest target paths with
`analysis/bin/flatten_genie_grid_outputs.sh` before the common analysis pass.
The detailed analysis instructions, including GENIE spline creation, are in
`analysis/README`.
